      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for those who prioritize functionality. Please be aware that the engine has a persistent, slow oil leak that will require monitoring or eventual repair, and the suspension is showing signs of age, leading to a somewhat stiffer ride. Despite these mechanical considerations, the interior is well-kept and the car starts consistently, making it a solid budget-friendly option.",
