    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a concours-level 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo. This unit features the legendary 2JZ-GTE inline-six with its sequential twin-turbocharging system intact and functioning at factory boost levels. Power is delivered through the bulletproof Getrag V160 6-speed manual gearbox to a Torsen limited-slip differential. The undercarriage is immaculate, showing original bushings and no signs of fluid weepage. All factory VIN stickers are present on the panels, confirming an accident-free history. Mechanical synchronization is flawless, with crisp gate engagement and a linear torque curve. A rare, unmolested example of JDM engineering excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
